utu (0.1.3-1~noble1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Restore src/tray.rs — blanked by the same rename commit that emptied
    main.rs; renames AyuzTray → UtuTray.
  * Fix adw::ViewStack API: remove set_transition_duration / set_enable_transitions
    (dropped in libadwaita 0.7+, unavailable on Noble's 1.5 package).
  * Fix zbus 5 compat: receive_brightness_changed() returns PropertyStream
    directly — remove stale Result match in oled_dimming.rs.
  * Fix GString conversion in gpu.rs: use &*t!() to deref Cow→&str for
    adw::AlertDialog heading/body builders.

